"Nigel Anthony Skeet" <naskeet(-at-)hotmail.com> wrote:
> Can any one tell me, in which back issues of Dune Buggies & Hot VWs, did the 
> various articles about "Project Westfalia" appear.   ...

Nigel,
The March 1990 edition featured part 6 of 6 in the Project Westfalia
series. Suspension is the topic of part 6.  It describes the resetting
of the rear torsion bar position, fitting shock absorbers and adding
anti-sway bars (front & rear) to a bus of approximately 1971 vintage.

Good luck,
